title: No, Barr Didn’t Call ‘Emergency Meeting’ after ‘Major’ Post-Election Discovery
subtitle: The year 2020 was challenging enough without junk news forcing us to travel backwards in time.
author: Jordan Liles
vclaim: Following the 2020 U.S. presidential election, Attorney General William Barr called an emergency meeting with President Donald Trump after a major voting ndiscovery was made.
